name: Tulip Fire
description: 011011•19•013435•698656  This generative piece was created by AI through careful selection of the piece’s parents (neither of whom were tulip or fire) and a guiding human hand, combining influence to create this unique and distinctive piece. Reminiscent of fluorescent gas fires, captured at a moment of beauty before being lost to vapour.  Minor colour adjustments were applied to prepare the piece for presentation.  This piece is 1/1 and will never be reproduced.  twitter / instagram: @autrecoeur
